&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Linear gradients&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Linear gradients in Highcharts have a similar syntax to that of SVG:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;color: {
    linearGradient: { x1: 0, x2: 0, y1: 0, y2: 1 },
    stops: [
        [0, '#003399'],
        [1, '#3366AA']
    ]
}&lt;/pre&gt;
